MID_支援_カミラ_スズカゼ_Ｃ: $a$t1$Wmカミラ|7$Wmスズカゼ|3$w0|$Wsカミラ|$WaSuzukaze, could I speak to\nyou for just a moment?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$WaPrincess Camilla... Yes, what is it?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|You're... often solicited by\nstrange women, aren't you?$k$pSo, I became most interested\nin what sort of person you are.$k$pWhy are you so popular, I wonder?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|...I say this so as not to\ninvite any misunderstanding...$k$pBut I basically reject such\nexcessive invitations.$k$pAnd I've occasionally received presents, but\nI'd decline them to the best of my ability.$k$pAlthough, there is no shortage of times\nto when I've been pushed into yielding...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|Hmm...$k$pStill, if that's the situation, you\nseem to respond so earnestly...$k$pAnd I wonder perhaps if that isn't\nthe reason why it is, on the contrary...$k$pWomen can't seem to leave you alone?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,|You suppose so...? Honestly,\nI can't understand it too well, but...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|I see... my interest has\nbeen piqued all the more.$k$pSoon, I want to hold a tea party\nwith the girls, including myself.$k$pI'll be most happy if you make\ncertain to come at that time.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E苦,|Th-that's...!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Now, now. It's important work to\ndeepen solidarity with the people$k$pof this army, don't you think?\nWe'll just have a chat, all right?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,|...I suppose this would be a command\ncoming from our leader's older sister?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|Yes, indeed... if you're going to come,\nyou may treat it as such.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,汗|I see... understood.\nIt seems you won't give up until I accept.$k$p...I'll intrude on your hospitality.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Haha, thanks.\nI'll be looking forward to it, then.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wd$w0|$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|…………$k
MID_支援_カミラ_スズカゼ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmスズカゼ|3$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|$w0|Hahhh...$k\n$Wmカミラ|7$w0|$Wsカミラ|$WaMy, why such a deep sigh, Suzukaze?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Ah... Princess Camilla, is it. This is,\nI suppose....it would be mental fatigue.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Can it be that the tea party I'd\ninvited you to was trying, perhaps?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E苦,|No... it's not so much as it was trying...$k$pBut that even the village women attended\nthe event in addition to the army's women...$k$pThe number of guests was\nmore than I was expecting...$k$pAnd I'm worn out from\nkeeping them company.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|Ahaha, the image of Suzukaze,\nsurrounded by girls...$k$pIt was quite a sight to see. All those cute\ngirls talking to you... I was a little jealous.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,汗|...If that's the case, Princess Camilla...$k$pIt would be great if you\nwould look after the women.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|But, while you say that, you kept\nthem perfectly entertained, didn't you?$k$pI was watching the situation, too, and you\nseemed to be happily talking with them, yes?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E苦,汗|That's... because it was your tea party.$k$pI bore in my mind not to do\nanything so discourteous.$k$pBesides, as long as someone's talking...$k$pI believe I should seriously\nlisten to what they have to say.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|Ahaha, even though you were in\nsuch a state... you can speak well.$k$pBut, I expect that seriousness\nand sincerity of yours...$k$pis connected to the reason you get hit on.\n...You know, I like you more and more.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,汗|Does that mean you want me\nto come to another tea party...?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|I just about want to decline, but... if it's\nan order, there's no question, is there?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|Ahaha, no matter where you are,\nyou're a serious person.$k$pWell, it's no longer an order. Once you\nreally want to come, that's when you should.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E苦,|Yes... understood.\nThen I'll take the liberty of doing that...$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wd$w0|$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Well, then... I wonder if he'll show up?$k
MID_支援_カミラ_スズカゼ_Ａ: $t1$Wmカミラ|7$Wmスズカゼ|3$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|$w0|Princess Camilla.$k$pThe other day, you said you would\nleave my attendance at your tea party...$k$pSolely up to my discretion, did you not...?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaYes, I did.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E苦,|Then why didn't you accept?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaI'm not really holding a tea party.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,|Well, then, why are you preparing\nenough tea for two here?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I wouldn't call this a tea party.\nI just wanted to talk with you.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|I'm glad that you're pleased with me but,\nwhat on earth do you want to talk about?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,|...The truth is, there was an\nincident I must thank you for.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,|What...?\nI don't recall having done anything...?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|I say that, though it's not\nme but my subordinates.$k$pAround the time they took part in\nthe army... From the beginning,$k$pmy subordinates clashed with the\nsoldiers on many occasions.$k$pThey were telling me that at those\ntimes, you'd helped them out.$k$pAlthough I didn't hear the full account,\nconsidering it's those girls...$k$pThey were unusually grateful...$k$p$E笑,|So I took an interest in you, too.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I see... but either way,\nI have no memory of this.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaHaha... surely, given how earnest you are,\nthat's a daily occurrence for you, isn't it?$k$pBut, thanks to that story, I had the great\nchance to become good friends with you.$k$p$Eキメ,|So I'm thankful.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E笑,|...Yes. That's true. That my friendship with\nyou has deepened makes me very happy.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaOh, what a lovely thing to say.$k$p$E笑,|Well then, from now on will you\naccompany me at teatime once in a while?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|Will it be tea with a lot of people?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaYes, it should be lively, shouldn't it?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E笑,汗|Heh... with what you've said up\nuntil now, I can no longer refuse.$k$pVery well. I will keep you company.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Haha, thank you.$k
MID_支援_カミラ_スズカゼ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmカミラ|7$Wmスズカゼ|3$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,|$w0|Here you go, Suzukaze.\nToday's tea is different than the usual.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E笑,|Thank you, Princess Camilla,\nthe flavor certainly is a little different.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaHaha, I take it you like it?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$WaYes. I think this black tea is wonderful.$k$p$E通常,|And come to think of it... until recently...$k$pI would never have expected that I would\nfrequently take tea with you like this.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E通常,|Indeed. It's the same for me.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,|When I met you in the beginning,\nI can honestly say...$k$pI did not know what\nyou were thinking.$k$p$E笑,|However, in talking with you like this,\nI have come to understand the truth...$k$pThat you are a very warm-hearted person.$k$pIt may be that people can't understand each\nother unless they come together to talk.$k$pNow, I truly am happy to\nbe able to meet with you.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E苦,|...I-indeed.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,|Princess Camilla, are you all right?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E怒,汗|…………$k$p...I simply wasn't expecting to hear\nsuch things from you face-to-face.$k$p$E怒,照|But, your words now make me very happy.\nIt's the first time I've felt like this...$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,汗|What...?$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,照|Before I even realized it, you seem to have\nbecome a very large presence in my life...$k$pI want to drink tea with you\nlike this every day from now on.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E怒,照汗|Princess Camilla... that is, I mean...$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Haha, shall I let you speak\nbeyond this point?$k$pIn a scene such as this, I'd like the\ngentleman to properly take the lead.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|...Understood. Then I will say it.$k$p$E怒,照|Princess Camilla, if it pleases you,\nwould you become my companion?$k$pI have been charmed by your personality\noverflowing with feelings of tolerance.$k$pOur social standings and\nhomelands differ, but...$k$pIf you will allow it, please let\nme protect you from now on.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$E笑,照|Thank you, Suzukaze.\nThose words... make me happy.$k$pI want to live together with you, too.\nLet's be together forever, shall we?$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$E笑,照|Yes...!$k\n$Wsカミラ|$WaHaha, I get jealous of the part of\nyou that's kind to all the ladies...$k$pBut, you have that faithful part of you that\noutweighs it as well... I do love that.$k$pSo, your confession\njust now stands the test.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$WaHaha, is that so.\nI am honored by your praise.$k\n$Wsカミラ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Well then, from now on, I'm in your care.$k\n$Wsスズカゼ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|Yes... Please be good to me,\nPrincess Camilla.$k
